OL,5, Boris Johnson has unveiled plans to    
OL,6, allow benefits to be put towards       
OL,7, mortgages in a speech relaunching his  
OL,8, premiership after a Tory revolt.       
OL,10,FThe PM made the "benefits to bricks"   
OL,11,Fpledge his first policy speech since   
OL,12,Fsurviving a bid to oust him.           
OL,14,FSpeaking in Blackpool, he also vowed to
OL,15,Fextend a scheme to allow social tenants
OL,16,Fto buy their homes.                    
OL,18,FBut critics say these are rehashed     
OL,19,Fideas that would make the housing      
OL,20,Fcrisis worse.                          
